{
  "video_id": "pTL1Bdhb2zo",
  "title": "Thoughts on John Carmack's Vision for Future VR | Game/Show | PBS Digital Studios",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 499.0,
      "end_time": 3185.0,
      "text": "[THEME MUSIC]"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7915.0,
      "end_time": 8990.0,
      "text": "Hey, everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8990.0,
      "end_time": 10180.0,
      "text": "Jamin here from &quot;Game/Show.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10180.0,
      "end_time": 11536.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here at the office."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11536.0,
      "end_time": 13160.0,
      "text": "And I just got back from San Francisco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13160.0,
      "end_time": 15842.0,
      "text": "where I was at the Game Developers Conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15842.0,
      "end_time": 16550.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16550.0,
      "end_time": 18258.0,
      "text": "If you ever get a chance to check it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18258.0,
      "end_time": 19374.0,
      "text": "you absolutely should go."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19374.0,
      "end_time": 21790.0,
      "text": "One of the things that I heard that was really interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21790.0,
      "end_time": 24810.0,
      "text": "was a talk by John Carmack, who-- I&#39;m sure a lot of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24810.0,
      "end_time": 26499.0,
      "text": "know-- is the creator of &quot;Doom.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26499.0,
      "end_time": 28040.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a very famous technical director"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28040.0,
      "end_time": 31060.0,
      "text": "who recently took a post running all the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31060.0,
      "end_time": 33889.0,
      "text": "for the Oculus Rift, which is a company that"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33889.0,
      "end_time": 34930.0,
      "text": "was acquired by Facebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 34930.0,
      "end_time": 36760.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re doing virtual reality technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 36760.0,
      "end_time": 39080.0,
      "text": "And he gave, gosh, an hour long plus"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 39080.0,
      "end_time": 43130.0,
      "text": "talk just sort of walking through his vision of what"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 43130.0,
      "end_time": 45589.0,
      "text": "virtual reality ostensibly will be like."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 45589.0,
      "end_time": 47880.0,
      "text": "I think there are a couple really interesting takeaways"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 47880.0,
      "end_time": 51000.0,
      "text": "from the talk, a lot which is incredibly technical"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 51000.0,
      "end_time": 53400.0,
      "text": "and definitely over my head."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 53400.0,
      "end_time": 55880.0,
      "text": "But there are two things I thought that was really, really"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 55880.0,
      "end_time": 57760.0,
      "text": "interesting in terms of framing how we should"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 57760.0,
      "end_time": 59200.0,
      "text": "think about virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 59200.0,
      "end_time": 62240.0,
      "text": "I think the first was, he had sort of made this point that--"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 62240.0,
      "end_time": 65069.0,
      "text": "and this is really strange for someone who had basically"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 65069.0,
      "end_time": 68580.0,
      "text": "cut his teeth as being the god of PC games"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 68580.0,
      "end_time": 71010.0,
      "text": "and being known as someone who&#39;s always pushing technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 71010.0,
      "end_time": 71690.0,
      "text": "forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 71690.0,
      "end_time": 74790.0,
      "text": "He made this really strong case that, in order for technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 74790.0,
      "end_time": 78144.0,
      "text": "like virtual reality to really make a significant debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78144.0,
      "end_time": 79560.0,
      "text": "it would have to reach essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 79560.0,
      "end_time": 83390.0,
      "text": "a billion people, which is roughly the size of Facebook&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 83390.0,
      "end_time": 84740.0,
      "text": "audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 84740.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "And the reason why is because, in order for a technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 88980.0,
      "text": "to really take cold, it has to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 88980.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "in the hands of as many people as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94330.0,
      "text": "And that sort of reminded me that, as popular"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 94330.0,
      "end_time": 97730.0,
      "text": "as virtual reality ostensibly has been amongst people"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 97730.0,
      "end_time": 100050.0,
      "text": "who play games-- obviously in technical communities--"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 100050.0,
      "end_time": 102675.0,
      "text": "most people haven&#39;t really tried it yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 102675.0,
      "end_time": 106130.0,
      "text": "And I think until it&#39;s in the hands of everyday people"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 106130.0,
      "end_time": 108544.0,
      "text": "like your mom, for example, it&#39;s going"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 108544.0,
      "end_time": 110210.0,
      "text": "to be really hard to tell whether or not"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110210.0,
      "end_time": 113080.0,
      "text": "virtual reality is the roaring success that it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 113080.0,
      "end_time": 114980.0,
      "text": "And I think the big revelation for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114980.0,
      "end_time": 117510.0,
      "text": "was that this idea that, for him, he"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117510.0,
      "end_time": 119880.0,
      "text": "was thinking of the future of VR experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119880.0,
      "end_time": 123520.0,
      "text": "was going to be these much smaller contained"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123520.0,
      "end_time": 125770.0,
      "text": "bite-sized experiences, not necessarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 125770.0,
      "end_time": 129881.0,
      "text": "these like big AAA type things that you might be accustomed"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 129881.0,
      "end_time": 130380.0,
      "text": "to."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 130380.0,
      "end_time": 132930.0,
      "text": "So the future is, again, for this guy who&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132930.0,
      "end_time": 135780.0,
      "text": "responsible for games like &quot;Doom,&quot; for him to essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 135780.0,
      "end_time": 137670.0,
      "text": "suggest that games like &quot;Flappy Bird&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 137670.0,
      "end_time": 139086.0,
      "text": "or things like that or going to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 139086.0,
      "end_time": 141740.0,
      "text": "pushing virtual reality forward is certainly a big concession."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141740.0,
      "end_time": 144031.0,
      "text": "I think the second big thing that they really dawned on"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 144031.0,
      "end_time": 146910.0,
      "text": "me actually came after I had a chance to try two"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 146910.0,
      "end_time": 149670.0,
      "text": "different Oculus experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 149670.0,
      "end_time": 154990.0,
      "text": "One was created by Weta, who did a lot of the visuals effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 154990.0,
      "end_time": 157192.0,
      "text": "for movies like &quot;The Hobbit,&quot; for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 157192.0,
      "end_time": 158650.0,
      "text": "And I tried an experience that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 158650.0,
      "end_time": 162100.0,
      "text": "did that was tied to the Smaug narrative from &quot;The Hobbit.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 162100.0,
      "end_time": 162980.0,
      "text": "It was really crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 162980.0,
      "end_time": 165990.0,
      "text": "And another one I did was one from Oculus Story Studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 165990.0,
      "end_time": 167690.0,
      "text": "It was a short called &quot;Lost,&quot; which"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 167690.0,
      "end_time": 170560.0,
      "text": "is about a hand that&#39;s lost in the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 170560.0,
      "end_time": 172800.0,
      "text": "I think that that made it pretty apparent that cinema"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 172800.0,
      "end_time": 175180.0,
      "text": "is going to be one of the big technologies driving"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 175180.0,
      "end_time": 177427.0,
      "text": "virtual reality forward in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 177427.0,
      "end_time": 179010.0,
      "text": "This idea, I think, before we&#39;re going"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 179010.0,
      "end_time": 181630.0,
      "text": "to get to a place to have interactive experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 181630.0,
      "end_time": 184030.0,
      "text": "I think we just need to have these passive &quot;being"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184030.0,
      "end_time": 185060.0,
      "text": "in a world&quot; experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 185060.0,
      "end_time": 188470.0,
      "text": "And again, these are not experiences that are yet"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 188470.0,
      "end_time": 189750.0,
      "text": "available to the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 189750.0,
      "end_time": 191940.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;ll link to them in description."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 191940.0,
      "end_time": 193730.0,
      "text": "One last thing, I think, before I go."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 193730.0,
      "end_time": 194850.0,
      "text": "I think one of my big concerns, certainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 194850.0,
      "end_time": 196600.0,
      "text": "on the virtual reality side, is that there"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 196600.0,
      "end_time": 199420.0,
      "text": "are a wide variety of different players right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 199420.0,
      "end_time": 200820.0,
      "text": "who are in the space."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 200820.0,
      "end_time": 201930.0,
      "text": "Gosh, there&#39;s so many."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 201930.0,
      "end_time": 202720.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s Oculus."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 202720.0,
      "end_time": 205680.0,
      "text": "And then HTC and Valve just announced the new one."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 205680.0,
      "end_time": 210330.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s an open source VR project."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 210330.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "Sony has Project Morpheus that&#39;s coming out."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 215440.0,
      "text": "Apple has filed patents for VR."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 215440.0,
      "end_time": 216910.0,
      "text": "I think for creators, until there&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 216910.0,
      "end_time": 221859.0,
      "text": "a single technology that&#39;s really unified"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 221859.0,
      "end_time": 223650.0,
      "text": "for all different types of creators to use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 223650.0,
      "end_time": 227160.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s going to be really, really tough to really see"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 227160.0,
      "end_time": 227752.0,
      "text": "things before."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 227752.0,
      "end_time": 229710.0,
      "text": "I think a really good analogy is the early days"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 229710.0,
      "end_time": 232280.0,
      "text": "of the web, when there were a variety of different browsers."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 232280.0,
      "end_time": 235400.0,
      "text": "And for a lot of you, you probably don&#39;t remember this."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 235400.0,
      "end_time": 237410.0,
      "text": "And it certainly before my time as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 237410.0,
      "end_time": 239868.0,
      "text": "There was a moment in time for the history of the web where"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 239868.0,
      "end_time": 242090.0,
      "text": "there was concern that each individual browser would"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 242090.0,
      "end_time": 243460.0,
      "text": "have its own set of standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 243460.0,
      "end_time": 245030.0,
      "text": "So if you have &quot;The New York Times,&quot; for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 245030.0,
      "end_time": 246850.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d have to make your web page differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 246850.0,
      "end_time": 249224.0,
      "text": "if it showed up on Internet Explorer, versus if it showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 249224.0,
      "end_time": 249870.0,
      "text": "up on Netscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 249870.0,
      "end_time": 252530.0,
      "text": "And there was this big meeting, a web standards summit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 252530.0,
      "end_time": 255320.0,
      "text": "where they made these decisions about, what is the technology?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 255320.0,
      "end_time": 258370.0,
      "text": "How are websites going to be displayed across all browsers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 258370.0,
      "end_time": 260290.0,
      "text": "I think, until virtual reality reaches"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 260290.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264230.0,
      "text": "a similar type of consensus about how things are made"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 264230.0,
      "end_time": 266030.0,
      "text": "and how old they&#39;re ultimately distributed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 266030.0,
      "end_time": 267696.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s going to be quite some time"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 267696.0,
      "end_time": 270050.0,
      "text": "before we really start to see the technology take off."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 270050.0,
      "end_time": 271790.0,
      "text": "But, hey, I could be wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 271790.0,
      "end_time": 273019.0,
      "text": "Anyway, that&#39;s all for now."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 273019.0,
      "end_time": 274810.0,
      "text": "Obviously very excited about all the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 274810.0,
      "end_time": 275950.0,
      "text": "that are happening in the world of VR."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 275950.0,
      "end_time": 276700.0,
      "text": "And yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 276700.0,
      "end_time": 278860.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll see you all next week."
    }
  ]
}